[p 
	"In 
	[em 
		"Kanshaku tamanage Kantarō no Tōkaidō Gojūsan-tsugi
	]em
	" (かんしゃく玉投げカン太郎の東海道五十三次), you play a fireworks-maker traveling the 
	[a class=extlink href=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T%C5%8Dkaid%C5%8D_%28road%29 rel=nofollow 
		"Tōkaidō road
	]a
	".  The game actually bears quite a resemblance to the actual geography of the Tōkaidō road; famous landmarks, rivers, and flora types are reproduced as well as they can be given the limitations of the Famicom.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The game is quite difficult --  the hero is slow moving and hard to control, and your only weapon is an endless supply of fireworks.  The 
	[a href=/3608S 
		"author's comments
	]a
	" detail the methods used as well as explaining all of the various baddies encountered during this quest.
